<div class="traveller-info">
  <div class="card m-1 border-warning px-0 border shadow-sm" style="background:#ffe475;">
    
    <div class="card-header py-1">
      <p class="h6 my-auto"><b><%= traveller.first_name %> <%= traveller.last_name.upcase %></b></p>
    </div>

    <div class="row h-100 no-gutters my-auto">
      <div class="col-12 my-auto py-2">

        Nom <%= traveller.first_name %>

        <div class="row no-gutters justify-content-center">

          <div class="col-4 px-1">
            <%= button_to edit_traveller_path(traveller), method: :get, remote: true, class: "btn btn-warning btn-block" do %>
              <p class="mb-0">Edit</p>
            <% end %>              
          </div>
          
          <div class="col-4 px-1">
            <%= button_to traveller, method: :delete, class:"btn btn-danger btn-block" do %>
              <p class="mb-0">Remove</p>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
        Anim pariatur cliche reprehenderit, enim eiusmod high life accusamus terry richardson ad squid. Nihil anim keffiyeh helvetica, craft beer labore wes anderson cred nesciunt sapiente ea proident.
    </div>
    
  </div>
</div>
